body:
Example:
```SystemVerilog
module demo (
	input [1:0] d,
	output reg [1:0] q,
	input s00, s01, s10, s11, en
);
	always_latch @* begin
		     if (s00) q = 2'b 00;
		else if (s01) q = 2'b 01;
		else if (s10) q = 2'b 10;
		else if (s11) q = 2'b 11;
		else if ( en) q = d;
	end
endmodule
```

`yosys -p 'verific -sv demo.sv; verific -import -gates demo; prep -flatten; splitnets -ports; clean -purge; show demo'`

